data.title: Weather in Borisovka, Tyumen Oblast, Russia data archive for October 30, 2015
data.meta_description: The past weather in Borisovka, Tyumen Oblast, Russia on October 30, 2015: temperature, wind, precipitation and relative air humidity
data.text:
Borisovka weather at night on October 30, 2015: overcast, no precipitation or weather events have been observed. The atmospheric pressure was normal. Air temperature -1…2°C. Southern moderate 10.8—14.4 km/h winds, wind gusts up to 39.6 km/h. Relative humidity 85—100%.

In the afternoon of October 30, 2015 Borisovka weather was as follows: overcast, slight rain, slight snow. The pressure was low. Air temperature 0…3°C. Southwestern moderate 7.2—18 km/h winds, wind gusts up to 39.6 km/h. Relative humidity 92—100%.

On this page you can find out what was the weather in Borisovka, Tyumen Oblast, Russia on October 30, 2015 according to the observation data of the weather station with the the World Meteorological Organization index 28573. Weather conditions are analyzed using an algorithm that determines the main weather parameters in Borisovka, Tyumen Oblast, Russia, such as air pressure, cloud cover, weather events, as well as ranges of air temperature, wind and humidity during the day.
